INSERT INTO `linkedin_given_recommendations` VALUES ('f1ac08dd7912fb56b9176afa3d9cc436','3344278','VSM','Vineet Seth, VSM','2014-06-17 10:02:05, Ashwin studied with Vineet Seth','','2014-06-17 10:02:05','Vineet thinks strategically, listens patiently, takes very balanced decisions and helps contribute to a great working atmosphere. His dedication to work is amazing and he goes about achieving his objectives with a steely resolve. Comes across with tremendous insight into how organisations work and how best to position them to derive effective results. His gentle demeanour and sincerity translates into long term relationships.','',94027037,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/vineetseth2/','541685051','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16'),('b195740acc9088765381420dd96f88c5','3344278','Agarwal','Minu Agarwal','2011-02-07 09:13:51, Ashwin managed Minu','','2011-02-07 09:13:51','Minu had to manage a number of projects and initiatives in Lotus Notes and later on CRM involving complex logistical and resourcing challenges. Minu is a quick learner and a great team player. She worked very hard, was always able to understand the bigger picture and get her priorities right - would love to work with her again.','',52981519,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/minu-agarwal-7278b015/','24033214','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16'),('295690ab6d403f165d8c6487914de6d4','3344278','Sundararajan','Suresh Sundararajan','2008-08-24 04:41:13, Ashwin managed Suresh','','2008-08-24 04:41:13','Suresh is a very talented, articulate and competent professional. He had worked with us very satisfactorily on several key and demanding project implementations across Africa in the Cards and Payment Switch domain. I would strongly recommend him.','',5359795,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/suresh-sundararajan-8979651/','5952889','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16'),('8fb395b260cb63bcbce31452a2236efd','3344278','Karekatte','Ajay Karekatte','2008-08-24 04:27:24, Ashwin managed Ajay','','2008-08-24 04:27:24','Ajay is easy-going, always approachable and posessess an affable personality.I see him as a confident leader good at setting directions for his team and motivating them to strive for stretched targets. His approach to all the assignments was professional and has left a deep impression on all the stakeholders he has engaged with.','',3417057,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ajaykarekatte/','5952791','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16'),('18f2271b775ee68cc80151e5e7572d0d','3344278','Devasy, PMP®, SAFe® Agilist','Ciby Devasy, PMP®, SAFe® Agilist','2008-08-02 00:25:57, Ashwin is client of Ciby','','2008-08-02 00:25:57','Ciby demonstrated good expertise in Lotus Notes support and development during his stint with us. His ability to identify / define scope and meet deadlines are some key qualities he possesses.','',6321646,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/cibyd/','5666927','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16'),('6bd38bfe1ae9aebe10a8519dc8a1e9cd','3344278','Agrawal','Mukul Agrawal','2007-07-19 14:11:56, Ashwin managed Mukul','','2007-07-19 14:11:56','Mukul was an important member of the team and was responsible for all phases of the transition and subsequent application ownership in Information Management domain. I was impressed with the depth of his technical skill set, project management capabilities specifically financial management, as well as his ability to consistently deliver clear, thoughtful strategic analysis to senior level management in business groups. Mukul is detail oriented, hard working, extremely smart, and a team player.','',2713965,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/mukulagrawal/','1985747','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16'),('8746f347de473a7c472b33263507abeb','3344278','Chandorkar','Aashish Chandorkar','2007-03-12 18:24:18, Ashwin senior than Aashish','','2007-03-12 18:24:18','Aashish is an individual with strong values. He is very well read and is always ready to share and apply his knowledge in new situations. The combination of his communication skills coupled with subject matter expertise helped him drive key messages which were important for delivery and implementation of a critical project.','',1034910,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/aashish/','1416980','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16'),('0438c89b1c594441370412ffd2cadc6a','3344278','Bedre','Sunil Bedre','2006-06-18 20:01:19, worked in same group','','2006-06-18 20:01:19','Sunil is a committed team member and is focussed towards the end goal without worrying about organisational hierachy and constraints. Sunil has ability to work under very tight deadlines and transnational teams. His expertise, focus, and ability to innovate have made him a tremendous asset to our team.','',3265958,'https://www.linkedin.com/in/sunilbedre/','82622','2018-03-08 07:58:22','2018-03-08 12:58:22','2018-03-20 07:21:16');
