INSERT INTO `linkedin_groups` VALUES ('d1a90e2ca8fef803dde02cc7c886f5d2','61057639','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=2291850&goback=','Banking Executives','16969','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAD4AAAAJDk4ZDE4ZDE4LTVjZDUtNDZhNy04ZDAyLWIzZmYyMGYzNzViYQ.png','2291850','This is designed for Professionals with skills or interest in Banking Executives','2018-03-08 05:32:31','2018-03-08 10:32:31','2018-03-08 05:32:31'),('ab83d3c7725b6a895dfdc016d0b36de6','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=48573&goback=','radRounds Radiology Network','26618','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAHNAAAAJDg0ZGMyNDEyLTA0MTQtNDA2OC04YmE4LTMxNmQ3ODU0YzY0Ng.png','48573','Linking medical imaging professionals, radiology, and radiologists globally to new opportunities, each other, and imaging expertise. For all those interested in diagnostic imaging, CT, MRI, x-ray technology, PET, nuclear medicine, ultrasound. Medical students, radiology technology students, radiology residents and other young aspiring professionals are welcome too to network and seek advice/networking. If you are in radiology - a radiologist, technologist, vendor, or business leader in medical imaging - join now!','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('b0e3fde96c64cc690f75d75c6ca3c23a','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=1866696&goback=','American College of Radiology (ACR)','21551','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAGAAAAAJDBlNjAzNDM5LWJjNjQtNDNhZS1hZDljLTg5ZDk2N2EyMDg3Yw.png','1866696','The 38,000 members of the American College of Radiology (ACR) include radiologists, radiation oncologists, medical physicists, interventional radiologists and nuclear medicine physicians. For over three quarters of a century, the ACR has devoted its resources to making imaging safe, effective and accessible to those who need it. The mission of the ACR is to serve patients and society by maximizing the value of radiology, radiation oncology, interventional radiology, nuclear medicine and medical physics by advancing the science of radiology, improving the quality of patient care, positively influencing the socio-economics of the practice of radiology, providing continuing education for radiology and allied health professions and conducting research for the future of radiology. The purpose of this group is to collaborate and share information about radiology. Members of this group may or may not be current ACR members. If you wish to confirm someone\'s membership with the ACR, please contact ACR Membership Services at 800-347-7748 or membership@acr.org. ACR reserves the right to remove any postings in this group which contain obvious solicitations or other materials that do not align with the objectives of this group or the ACR\'s mission.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('e12d1471db701f3f7a0349fe02dda414','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=4250722&goback=','Jack Welch Management Institute (JWMI) Networking Group','7650','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAckAAAAJDFhNWJjZmQ0LWQwMzAtNGIxNS05NjU0LWU3OGQ0YWRhOTFhZQ.png','4250722','The Jack Welch Management Institute (JWMI) Student Networking Group is for students, alumni and faculty of the Jack Welch Management Institute\'s Executive MBA or Executive Certificate programs at Strayer University. We invite you to use this group to keep in touch with classmates and professors, as well as make new connections. When requesting to join, please include your association with the Jack Welch Management Institute.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('b972a19344b3323c2eb8b634bd9ef570','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=2547755&goback=','Society of Nuclear Medicine and Molecular Imaging (SNMMI)','12753','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAADzAAAAJDk5MjQ3NjI3LTlhOTMtNDQxNy04ZDZmLTlkOWJmOGY1MDE3Ng.png','2547755','SNMMI is an international scientific and medical association dedicated to raising public awareness about how nuclear medicine and molecular imaging can help provide patients with the best health care possible. SNMMI members specialize in nuclear medicine and molecular imaging—a vital element of today’s medical practice that adds an additional dimension to diagnosis and therapy, changing the way common and devastating diseases are understood and treated. SNMMI’s more than 17,000 members set the standard for molecular imaging and nuclear medicine practice by creating guidelines, sharing information through journals and meetings and leading advocacy on key issues that affect molecular imaging and therapy research and practice. Members of the group include physicians, technologists, scientists and other professionals related to the discipline.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('4b2aec5fa7aede5ef6f5cda36519b30e','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=4869208&goback=','Best IVF Clinics Chennai','42','','4869208','Prime OBG Fertility Center in Chennai is famous for female fertility. Treatment with latest infertility treatments and have very high success rates and recognized as one of the best fertility centre in Chennai.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('0ecbe9ec6f3b454618c71db7e1b8fd7c','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=3066514&goback=','Hospital and Healthcare Operations Executives Forum','8957','','3066514','This is a group for Operations Professionals and Executives in the Hospital and Healthcare Service Provider Sector, to share industry related information, discuss relevant topics, current issues, healthcare reform, and assist each other with career growth and professional development. Recruiting Professionals requests to join will be declined.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('57fcf938007ff3c593fbb709fa216576','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=2166770&goback=','Musculoskeletal (MSK) imaging','3156','','2166770','For discussion of all things related to MSK Radiology','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('d534508fd1e14827f96bcb9ad6c03d82','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=3394310&goback=','NSGC - National Society of Genetic Counselors','2853','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAACJAAAAJGRkYTUyNzM2LTljNmEtNDlmYy05NDYzLTg1Y2U3Y2ZhYzcyYQ.png','3394310','The Society\'s Vision: Integrating genetics and genomics to improve health for all. The Society\'s Mission: The National Society of Genetic Counselors advances the various roles of genetic counselors in health care by fostering education, research, and public policy to ensure the availability of quality genetic services. The Society promotes the professional interests of genetic counselors and provides a network for professional communications. Local and national continuing education opportunities and the discussion of all issues relevant to human genetics and the genetic counseling profession are an integral part of belonging to the NSGC.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('6b67e37500d0e24c4827f8c8fb1c5783','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=2166749&goback=','Neuroradiology','3042','','2166749','For all interested in Neuroradiology','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('32c875e936dae695a664cd8a3d59f7f5','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=4306800&goback=','Radiology jobs','2728','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAD1AAAAJDNlMWJhNzY3LTQ3NTUtNGZmOS05ZjRhLTYyZTk0MWI2M2ZiNA.png','4306800','Find the job of you dreams by joining the Radiology jobs group!','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('e7d63daf2187381f95a794570d14de0f','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=1941465&goback=','Radiolopolis - professional Radiology community for education, research and clinical practice','5128','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAFWAAAAJDNkMzg4YTU3LWRkOTUtNDI0Yi04YmY2LTI5NDdiYmEzOWE1OQ.png','1941465','This Radiology community for education, research and practice connects Radiology professionals from all over the world. It helps to: - Find and connect to people with similar interests and expand your network - Discuss Radiology topics in dedicated forums - from residency to practice - Simplify your research and find partners - Create or join research and study groups - General and Radiology specific search engines - Read Radiology news from multiple subspecialties - Publishing case reports (collaboration with the JRCR) - Find helpful tools for your daily work (calculators, case tracker, research tools, etc.) - Prepare for the Radiology boards - Find tutorials and eLearning material - Share your images, videos, teaching files and lectures The founders of Radiolopolis developed in the past years several educational and clinical / practical programs (see image above), which where running separately. We recognized, that the full power of these programs can be best utilized when combined. That\'s how the idea of \"Radiolopolis\" was born. We will continuosly add and incorporate more programs into Radiolopolis, so that they can be seamlessly used by our \"citizens\" directly from this website. Radiolopolis is one of the most sophisticated and comprehensive professional networks for Radiology in the web, combining multiple awarded educational, clinical and research programs.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('1c11dbba81dd325898730dd7bcbf2770','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=1058287&goback=','Strayer University','9240','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAADPAAAAJDhjNDY2ZTVlLTc2ZjgtNDgxYy1hMTFlLTcyNzZiYTg3NzVmZg.png','1058287','Welcome to the Strayer University LinkedIn group. At Strayer University we are committed to helping our students and alumni connect with each other, whether on campus or online. That\'s why we\'ve created this group, to help make it easier for you to network and keep in touch with fellow students, faculty or friends. For more than 115 years, Strayer University has been dedicated to helping working professionals achieve their education and career goals. Get to know our Strayer community - join our LinkedIn group today! For more information about all of our program offerings, visit - http://www.strayer.edu/ You can also find us at: www.facebook.com/strayeruniversity www.twitter.com/strayeru www.youtube.com/user/StrayerUniversity','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('f2f8c0a5f21ee375fd2783501b40bf10','75543705','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=2376172&goback=','The British Institute of Radiology - BIR','1478','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAADTAAAAJDVhNDU0OGUwLTU2N2QtNDIyYy1hYTRiLTc2M2JjNmQwOTNiNA.png','2376172','The British Institute of Radiology is the international membership organisation for everyone working in imaging, radiation oncology and the underlying sciences.collaboration and the sharing of knowledge and understanding. We aim to: Support the work of our members and their colleagues to achieve professional excellence Provide continuing professional development for our multidisciplinary community Publish cutting edge research for our authors and readers across the world Influence and connect with the wider professional sector.','2018-03-08 06:25:13','2018-03-08 11:25:13','2018-03-08 06:25:13'),('3c15d72b15c16d3ae9e56f42bdad3fa0','3344278','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=54066&goback=','Marketing, Sales, Social Media and PR Innovators Innovation Network by the InnovationAssocation.org','608434','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMAAQCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAA2IAAAAJDczYTA3YTAyLTE0OGMtNDQzZS1iMzIzLTM0YWNjNTcyNTdiNg.png','54066','Join the LARGEST MARKETING INNOVATION GROUP on Linkedin. Learn, network and share ideas with 500,000 innovative marketing, sale