ies and Novantas is a formidable team in both bank and corporate treasury markets. For more information about Treasury Strategies go to www.TreasuryStrategies.com For more information about Novantas go to www.Novantas.com','2018-03-08 07:57:18','2018-03-08 12:57:18','2018-03-08 07:57:18'),('55df437f362d8fc9d22289fcd3f129eb','3344278','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=64064&goback=','Payments Strategy','47503','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAADYAAAAJDVhM2RiMThjLTM3NzQtNDFhMS05YjM3LWY3MmJmZDViZDQ0Nw.png','64064','Group for professionals currently or previously involved with Payments, in any function including strategy and product development. Payments can include anything from credit cards to cash to check to banking systems (ACH, Wire, etc...) and alternative forms of payment (mobile, digital, NFC, Blockchain, e-wallets, etc...) from competitors such as traditional banks, PayPal, Google, Apple, Amazon, new Fintech companies etc....','2018-03-08 07:57:18','2018-03-08 12:57:18','2018-03-08 07:57:18'),('a8fc51a34dfef357176023aac6a3ec66','3344278','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=54235&goback=','India Leadership Network','214306','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAE3AAAAJGQ3YmM5Yzk2LTRhNjctNDRjOS1hODBiLTgyZmZmMjBlNzkwMQ.png','54235','A vision to connect all believing in leadership, and to join hands for impactful achievements. Our mission is to create 100,000 leaders in life, society and organizations who can create sustained transformation. Join us','2018-03-08 07:57:18','2018-03-08 12:57:18','2018-03-08 07:57:18'),('68b8d0cee326d59815ccde5afdfa6d7c','3344278','https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=123111&goback=','LEAN THINKING','24895','https://media.licdn.com/media/AAMB_wCJAAIAAQAAAAAAAAEAAAAAJDYzNzQ0MWFkLTAwNjQtNGIwMC05MjMxLTkyMWJlMjdhYjk1MA.png','123111','This is a group for people who have a LEAN thinking and want to interact with others to share ideas and discuss their experiences.','2018-03-08 07:57:18','2018-03-08 12:5